short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Never confuse the Covid19-Variant with the holding company's name ever again.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Omicron, the Covid19-Variant, and Omnicom, the global advertising holding company, are easily confused. That's why this extension appends "not Omnicom" to every written instance of "Omicron" in your web browser.

Made by Till B.
